  "description": "This individual presents as an animated corpse, with light skin drawn tight over sharp bone ridges and a permanently slack jawline. Black hair hangs in an unkempt fall, thinning at the crown and matted along the temples. Yellow eyes sit deep in the sockets, fixed in an unblinking stare that reads as predatory rather than alert. The hands show rigid, tendon-bared contours, with fingertips worn down to blunt, stained nails from habitual scraping and clawing.",
